---
title: Cauliflower Bacon Mac 'N' Cheese with Cavatappi and Scallions
description: Bacon. Mac ’n’ cheese. Need we say more? Okay, how about gooey, melty, bouncy, smoky, savory, and cascading with curls of cavatappi? Not convinced? Well, there’s a good amount of calcium-rich cauliflower in there too—roasted, not boiled, to bring out its natural sweetness and give it a crisp-edged tenderness that is sure to please.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2018w52r14-cauliflower-bacon-mac-n-cheese-46740c9c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2018w52r14-cauliflower-bacon-mac-n-cheese-5be4547330006c4ca56a9b82-12bbabe8.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cauliflower-bacon-mac-n-cheese-5be4547330006c4ca56a9b82
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 710 kcal
  fat: 26 g
  saturated fat: 12 g
  carbohydrates: 85 g
  sugar: 12 g
